node.text:
Our friends over at @Classicdadmoves helped us celebrate the ultimate golf dad with all the Chili’s food and some ice cold @michelobultra - just in time for Father’s Day! 

Keep an eye out - we might just have an epic Father’s Day giveaway coming your way!

node.text: Now, when you grab a dad-sized bite at Chili’s, you’re doing it for a great cause. How? We partnered with @classicdadmoves & kids @stjude to help raise awareness (and money, too). node.text: Get in on a job where food and fun are always on the clock! If you love awesome perks and having fun at work, then you’re a perfect fit for our Chilihead team. We’re proud to offer our team members medical benefits, no-cost GED & Associates Degrees, tuition assistance and even discounted meals! Apply today for our available full-time, part-time and manager positions at the link in bio..
